  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this pilot study is to investigate the effect of an oral nutritional
      supplement (preOP booster) versus placebo regarding metabolic criteria in patients undergoing
      elective pancreaticoduodenectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
